These are Puzzles for 2x2 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-1::.
Birthday: november, june
Transport: car, train
1. Transport:car is in an even position##4
2. Transport:train == Birthday:june##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |     2      |
| Birthday   | june | november |
| Transport     | train    | car   |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-2::.
Transport: motorbike, tram
Food: spinach, cherry
1. Food:spinach is in an odd position##4
2. Transport:tram is on the left of Transport:motorbike##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |       2       |
| Transport   | tram | motorbike        |
| Food      | spinach  | cherry |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-3::.
Pet: guinea-pig, turtle
Sport: water-polo, badminton
1. Sport:water-polo is in an odd position##4
2. Pet:turtle is on the left of Pet:guinea-pig##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |
| Pet   | turtle    | guinea-pig |
| Sport   | water-polo | badminton |

